videos.headline: Rachwal takes fake punt for big gain
videos.description: Eastern Michigan pulls out a trick play as Kyle Rachwal gains 27 yards on the fake punt.

videos.headline: Western Michigan capitalizes on INT with TD

videos.headline: Fricano misses game-tying FG
